Package graph

Class Graph

  • java.lang.Object
    • graph.Graph
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GraphInterface
    public class Graph
extends java.lang.Object
implements GraphInterface
    Class that saves all the information about the graph, including the number of node, the nest and implements the adjacency list and the respective methods.
    Author:
    Pedro Mendes, Rui Livramento, Francisco Costa
